<div id="content">
    <div>
        <h3>About</h3>
        <div class="first">
            <a href="#"><img src="~/Images/SudhirV2.png" alt="" class="img-rounded welcomeimg" /></a>
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>
                <span class="Three-Dee-normal" style="font-size:20px;">SF<sup>2</sup></span> is registered public charitable trust (Reg No. - Serial No. : 6660 / Book No. :- 4 / Deed No. :- 6 / Government of Bihar) formed to establish
